With every moment that has passed

277
00:26:48,635 --> 00:26:50,830
Oh Señorita

278
00:26:52,539 --> 00:26:55,372
You've managed to win my heart

279
00:26:55,775 --> 00:26:57,640
And that's all there is to it

280
00:26:58,345 --> 00:27:00,370
Don't look away

281
00:27:02,282 --> 00:27:04,443
Stay close to me

