01:04:15,613 --> 01:04:18,316
If you're carrying
your restlessness in your heart

814
01:04:18,316 --> 01:04:20,375
You are alive

815
01:04:20,451 --> 01:04:23,011
If you're carrying
the lightning of dreams in your eyes

816
01:04:23,087 --> 01:04:24,281
You are alive

817
01:04:25,590 --> 01:04:28,582
Like a gust of wind,
learn to live free

818
01:04:29,260 --> 01:04:32,229
Learn to flow like
the waves that make a sea

